output.text: At the beginning of the game, when the three starter Pokemon spawn, you can walk away from them in order to have a Pikachu spawn nearby. Then, you will be able to catch a Pikachu as your starter.

By using a Lucky Egg while evolving or hatching Pokémon, you can gain experience points twice as fast than if you had done the same things without a Lucky Egg. While evolving normally gives 500 XP, doing so while under the influence of a Lucky Egg gives 1000 XP instead (not including evolving into a new Pokémon).
